ğŸ§  About

AI Resume & Portfolio Builder is an easy-to-use tool that uses AI and NLP techniques to help students and freshers create professional resumes, cover letters, and portfolio websites automatically. It analyzes skills, projects, and target job roles to generate polished and recruiter-friendly documents and pages.

