ğŸ“¦ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Backend: Python, FastAPI

AI/ML: NLP, TF-IDF, cosine similarity

Deployment: Docker, Nginx

Most components are implemented using plain Python with no paid AI APIs required, helping you learn core techniques while building something real.

